  "prompt": "What hotel in Dharamshala Hill-station would be safe for unmarried couples, without the harassment of police, hotel staff, and moral police?",
  "response": "When traveling as an unmarried couple to Dharamshala, you\u2019ll want to choose a hotel that is known for being couple-friendly and respectful of privacy. Here are some well-regarded options that are known for being safe for unmarried couples:\n\n1. **Hotel Inclover** - Located in the heart of Dharamshala with modern amenities and a focus on guest privacy.\n2. **Quartz Himalayan Brothers** - Known for its welcoming environment and stunning views.\n3. **The Divine Hima** - A boutique hotel providing excellent service and ensuring guest comfort.\n4. **The Pavilion** - Popular for its luxurious ambiance and attentive staff.\n5. **Hotel Snow Crest Inn** - Offers a pleasant stay with a friendly staff that respects guest privacy.\n\nWhen booking, make sure to confirm the hotel\u2019s couple-friendly policy. Websites like MakeMyTrip, OYO Rooms, and Goibibo often indicate whether a hotel is couple-friendly. It\u2019s also beneficial to check recent reviews online to ensure good experiences from other unmarried couples.",
